readme:
Hubot Dogeme
============

Wow. Such Doge. So Hubot.


Install
-------

- Add `hubot-dogeme` to your Hubot's `package.json`
- Add `hubot-dogeme` to your Hubot's `external-scripts.json`
- Wow. Such install.


Commands
--------

`hubot doge me` - Get a doge  
`hubot doge bomb <n>` - Get \<n\> doges
